#### 2. Early-return guard flattens delete handler nesting
**File**: `apps/api/src/routes/recipes.ts:34-44`
**Type**: Reduced nesting
**Before**:
```ts
const recipe = await prisma.recipe.findUnique({ where: { id: req.params.id } });
if (recipe) {
  if (recipe.ownerId === req.user.id) {
    await prisma.recipe.delete({ where: { id: req.params.id } });
    res.status(204).send();
  } else {
    res.status(403).json({ error: 'Forbidden' });
  }
} else {
  res.status(404).json({ error: 'Recipe not found' });
}
```
**After**:
```ts
const recipe = await prisma.recipe.findUnique({ where: { id: req.params.id } });
if (!recipe) return res.status(404).json({ error: 'Recipe not found' });
if (recipe.ownerId !== req.user.id) return res.status(403).json({ error: 'Forbidden' });
await prisma.recipe.delete({ where: { id: req.params.id } });
res.status(204).send();
```

